        <Parent_String>Myriapoda (subphylum) [300310467], Arthropoda (phylum) [300265687], Animalia (kingdom) [300249395], Eukaryota (domain) [300265677], living organisms (entities) [300390503], Living Organisms (hierarchy name) [300265673], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
